  "text": "The main challenge with the approach from Chen et al. is that to address the forward problem, a CT scan is required. This means that this method can only be used for monitoring since for it to be effective there must be an original image from CT [CITATION_1] . Therefore, a priori information of the test object is required for the fusion techniques. Usually a technique with good spatial information (such as MRI, CT), etc., is fused with a technique like EIT with good temporal information [CITATION_2] .",
